==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obtenebration
<hw>Ob*ten`e*bra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>obtenebrate</ets> to make dark.]</ety> <def>The act of darkening;
the state of being darkened; darkness.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In every megrim or vertigo, there is an <qex>obtenebration</qex>
joined with a semblance of turning round.</q>
<rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obtension</ent>⟦br⟧
